      "created_at": "2017-05-26T09:40:35.167Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Po ta mendosh mire, keto çudira te mbajne gjalle instiktet primare, te forcojne imunitetin…dmth nuk jane dhe aq keq. Se jashte te behet monotone qetesia, rruget pa gropa, ulen antenat fare, s’ka mikrobe shume <img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/images/emoji/apple/thinking.png?v=5\" title=\":thinking:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":thinking:\">, hiç sherre koti.</p>",
      "reply_to_post_number": null,
      "like_count": 0
